  "id": "RAW_eb5cd3",
  "title": "被低估的 Claude Code：AI Native 软件开发的关键拼图",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/azPxvI4GSVEWe49dplWd5Q",
  "date": "2025-02-25 06:33:31",
  "author": "Yan Wang",
  "siteName": "十字路口Crossing",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <section>\n   <section style=\"margin:0px 0px 20px;border-right:1px dashed rgb(50, 120, 71);white-space:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;line-height:26px;border-bottom:1px dashed rgb(50, 120, 71);\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;font-size: 15px;\">\n     <section style=\"width: 90%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0px 0px 10px;border-color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-size: 15px;\">\n      <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;font-size: 15px;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🚥</span></p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"padding: 0px 12px 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);letter-spacing: 0.1em;font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;color: rgb(55, 53, 47);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Koji 按: 昨天 Anthropic 发布 Claude 3.7，全网热议。我第一时间在 Cursor 试用 Claude 3.7，有种「通电感」。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;color: rgb(55, 53, 47);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果说 3.5 还只是在代码基础上做增补（像一个中级工程师），那么 3.7 已经可以完成一定程度的系统架构设计啦（进化到架构设计师，这是质的飞跃）。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;color: rgb(55, 53, 47);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在今天的文章中，Yan Wang 分享了 Anthropic 与 Claude 3.7 同时发布的 Claude Code。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;min-height: 20px;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"margin:20px 0px;border-right:1px dashed rgb(50, 120, 71);white-space:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;line-height:26px;border-bottom:1px dashed rgb(50, 120, 71);\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;font-size: 15px;\">\n     <section style=\"width: 90%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0px 0px 10px;border-color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-size: 15px;\">\n      <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;font-size: 15px;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🚥</span></p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"padding: 0px 12px 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);letter-spacing: 0.1em;font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;color: rgb(55, 53, 47);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Yan Wang</span></span><span leaf=\"\">: 奥运火炬手，私人飞行员，咖啡烘焙师，常春藤博士。个人网站：</span><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Computing Life</span><sup style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">[1]</span></sup></strong></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;min-height: 20px;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic 昨天发布了</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude 3.7</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，吸引了媒体的广泛关注。不过，大多数人似乎忽略了同时推出的另一个工具——</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。这个命令行工具看起来不那么引人注目，界面也不够人性化，没有像 Cursor 或 Devin 那样高调宣称要自我进化甚至取代人类程序员。</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:10px 10px 10px 20px;word-spacing:normal;overflow:auto;color:rgb(106, 115, 125);font-weight:400;border-left:3px solid rgb(50, 120, 71);display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding: 0px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);margin: 0px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但当我深入了解后才意识到，Claude Code 这个看似普通的工具可能恰恰是推动 AI Native 软件开发革命的关键，甚至有可能深刻影响未来的商业模式和生态系统。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;min-height: 20px;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501607249\" data-ratio=\"0.6464\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fbb05fa7-0555-42dc-cb52-d53b8ecdfe00/public\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1250\" style=\"border-radius: 8px;font-size: 15px;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fbb05fa7-0555-42dc-cb52-d53b8ecdfe00/public\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <h2 style=\"padding:0px;margin:40px auto 40px 0px;font-weight:bold;background:linear-gradient(rgb(255, 255, 255) 80%, rgb(50, 120, 71) 20%);width:fit-content;font-size:20px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">从传统模式到 AI Friendly 开发</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在我们介绍和推广 Agentic AI 的过程中，经常收到针对 Cursor 这样的 AI 编程工具的反馈是：这些工具对于快速做原型、辅助写一些脚本或者进行数据分析的 ad-hoc 的任务可以完成得很好。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但是，只要涉及到大型项目或者已有的成熟的代码库，AI 就经常卡壳</span></span><span leaf=\"\">——它往往找不到最相关的文件和函数接口，也不了解相关的开发规范和最佳实践，更不用说去理解每个设计的高层决策过程甚至历史包袱了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但这实际上是一个很关键的问题。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">很多企业手里都有十几万行、甚至上百万行的内部核心代码，光是列出依赖、结构、文档就够人喝一壶，别说让 AI 一次性学完。于是 AI 在小项目里大显身手，却对企业最关键的系统无从下手。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果我们没办法解决对接已有代码库这个问题，AI 开发就只能停留在辅助开发或者原型构建上，而不能真的用于大型、严肃和最具有商业价值的项目里。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而如果我们能解决让 AI 正确且高效地使用已有的代码库这个问题，下面整个领域的发展可能就一日千里。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们可以看见 AI 主导的软件开发在各个领域迅速落地。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因此从某种程度上说，AI 开发正面临一个鸿沟，一边是 AI 自主开发软件的美好愿景，一边则是 AI 还没办法利用大多数私有代码库的现实困境。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但说句公道话，这其实不是 AI 自己的问题。我们之前也</span><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">多次讨论过</span><sup style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">[2]</span></sup></strong><span leaf=\"\">，</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 要想有效地完成任何任务（不仅限于编程），前提是它要有足够的背景知识。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">就好比你新招了一个实习生，如果直接扔给他几百个文件的代码库，就指望他立刻写出正确高效的代码，这本身就是强人所难。更好的方法是给他一个入职培训，让他理解整个库的函数，结构，设计甚至历史。经过这样的培训，实习生写出高质量代码的成功率就会大幅提升。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于 AI 来说，这种入职培训的具体形式往往是给它一个现成的 prompt 文件。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">例如，Model Context Protocol (MCP)这个项目就在</span><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个 URL</span><sup style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">[3]</span></sup></strong><span leaf=\"\">里提供了这样的 prompt 文件。如果你把这个 prompt 文件扔给 AI（比如 ChatGPT 或者 Cursor），它就会有足够的背景知识来写出正确的代码。目前这个 prompt 文件的构建很多时候仍然是一个半自动甚至手动的过程。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">例如，我们可以把一个库里所有函数的 docstring 全部扔给 ChatGPT，让它筛选出最重要的函数，然后写出一个 Markdown 的文档，作为 AI 的 prompt 使用。在这种文档的支持下，对于中小规模的项目，AI 就可以轻松写出正确的程序了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以，到这一步为止，我们已经看见了</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">两种不同的软件开发模式：</span></span></p>\n   <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;padding-left: 1.5em;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;vertical-align: baseline;white-space: normal;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin-bottom: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;list-style-position: outside;\">\n     <p style=\"border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 15px;line-height: inherit;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;margin: 10px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一种传统模式是软件开发的 deliverable 就是代码本身，最多加一个给人类看的文档。</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;font-variant-numeric: inherit;font-variant-east-asian: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;list-style-position: outside;\">\n     <p style=\"border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: inherit;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: 15px;line-height: inherit;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但是，另一种新的思路是 AI friendly 的软件开发。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">它强调软件开发的交付物不仅是针对人类交付，同时是针对 AI 交付。所以，在代码本身和针对人类的文档之外，往往还会包含一个针对 AI 的 prompt 文件。它的好处是让 AI 可以迅速上手，用这个库直接写出正确的程序。</span></p></li>\n   </ol>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">随着 Cursor 等工具的逐渐流行，</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">软件开发是否 AI friendly 的重要性也越来越高。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">例如，你是一个公司的技术领导，面对两个库要做技术选型。一个库直接拿过来用 Cursor 就能上手写程序，另一个库你还要去做各种学习和处理，才能在 AI 的辅助下一点一点写。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">前者在市场上的竞争优势是不言而喻的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;min-height: 20px;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501607247\" data-ratio=\"0.7744565217391305\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8678fcb3-0f5b-43e6-7771-cb2af99efd00/public\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"736\" style=\"border-radius: 8px;font-size: 15px;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8678fcb3-0f5b-43e6-7771-cb2af99efd00/public\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <h2 style=\"padding:0px;margin:40px auto 40px 0px;font-weight:bold;background:linear-gradient(rgb(255, 255, 255) 80%, rgb(50, 120, 71) 20%);width:fit-content;font-size:20px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">21st.dev，Library as a Service，和 AI Native 开发</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI friendly 的软件开发模式，虽然相比于传统的软件开发模式有了长足进步，但是它离引发整个软件开发领域的革新，仍然有着相当大的距离。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了理解这一点，我们先看一下</span></span><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">21st.dev</span><sup style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">[4]</span></sup></strong><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个网站。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">21st.dev 这个网站或者说软件库很有意思。它本质上是一个 UI 库，提供了很多前端组件。但和传统的软件库的使用方法不同，它不是把所有的组件交付给用户，让用户来学习和写代码，而是反过来，让用户告诉它想构建什么东西，它来选择调用什么样的 UI 组件来为用户构建一个前端。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">换言之，它的 deliverable 不是一个类库，而是用户需要的代码本身，这个代码里面包含了相关的类，用户也可以在拿到以后自行更改。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这其实是一种新的使用库的方法，Library as a Service（LaaS）。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">软件库的交付物不是代码，不是文档，而直接变成了一种服务，一个 API。对用户/开发体验来说，这是一个重大的改变。因为就算是 AI Friendly 的模式，在实际开发中，这个 prompt 文件也还是需要开发者自己撰写和维护，对团队在文档管理、版本控制、prompt 撰写等方面提出了很多要求。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因此，即使是 AI Friendly 这种开发模式，也往往只是在原有写代码—打包—部署的流水线里做局部改进，并没有颠覆性地改变交付模式。而 LaaS 就不一样了，它从“我交付的是 API+背后的 AI 执行力”这个逻辑出发，把商业和技术交付捆绑在一起，彻底改变了怎么收费、怎么对外演示、怎么迭代升级。如果说传统的软件库交付的是建筑材料，LaaS 交付的就是一个包工包料的施工团队，重构了软件开发的价值链。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501607250\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/19b0b2cc-9d89-43b9-3eed-3b7969421b00/public\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1920\" style=\"border-radius: 8px;font-size: 15px;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/19b0b2cc-9d89-43b9-3eed-3b7969421b00/public\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在用户体验升级之外，LaaS 对提供库的企业来说，也有很大的好处。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一方面，这让企业有了更大的控制力和自主权，对外可以鼓励用户在使用库的时候应用最佳实践，对内可以做出更综合更高效的优化。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">另一方面，从收费的角度来说，它提供的这种附加值服务也可以带来超额盈利，让传统意义上一次交付的软件库变成了一只持续下金蛋的鸡。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从整个软件开发的领域来说，LaaS 这种方法带来了巨大的想象空间。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">如果未来我们的软件库都以 LaaS 的方法交付的话，AI 利用这些库来进一步构建软件的过程会变得特别简单和流畅。它更多的是起一个 planner 统筹规划的作用，只需要根据每个库擅长的领域决定什么问题用什么库就可以了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">接下来，具体利用这些库来写代码则完全可以使用每个库的服务，利用 API 调用来完成。</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从某种层面上说，这也可以被称为 Library as an Agent。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">这样我们就把一个复杂的利用多个软件库的软件开发流程，变成了一个 multi-agent 合作、迭代的问题。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样就可以解决我们在上一章开头提出的问题。如果有了 LaaS，通过把库的学习和使用完全 delegate 给库的作者构建的 agent，Agentic AI 就不再是只能解决 adhoc 问题的玩具，而可以灵活高效地适配已有的企业级的软件库。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种开发方法相比于传统的方法，甚至 AI friendly 的方法，是更加 AI native 的。虽然 Agentic AI 仍然是一个非常新的东西，我们在目前还很难预测未来软件开发最终会收敛到怎样的形式上去。</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:10px 10px 10px 20px;word-spacing:normal;overflow:auto;color:rgb(106, 115, 125);font-weight:400;border-left:3px solid rgb(50, 120, 71);display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding: 0px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);margin: 0px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但是我们基本可以肯定，最终大家都采用的一定是一种 AI native 的方法——所有技术手段围绕 AI 来设计，作为 AI enabler 来尽可能提升 AI 的工作效率这样的技术框架。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"501607248\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3b0a130c-f08d-4a26-d0da-d63981b6db00/public\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"2048\" style=\"border-radius: 8px;font-size: 15px;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3b0a130c-f08d-4a26-d0da-d63981b6db00/public\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">LaaS 的愿景虽然美好，但它的实现门槛仍然很高。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如，如何在代码生成的过程中引入 Agentic Workflow，来实现自我迭代、自我更正，从而保证生成的代码质量。这需要相当多的实战经验和对 LLM 的深刻理解。我们只要看一下开源的 Cline 和 Cursor 之间的性能差距，就容易理解了。</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:10px 10px 10px 20px;word-spacing:normal;overflow:auto;color:rgb(106, 115, 125);font-weight:400;border-left:3px solid rgb(155, 215, 25);display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding: 0px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);margin: 0px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但 Claude Code 的出现正好填补了这个空白，极大地降低了 LaaS 的实现难度。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">具体来说，Claude Code 提供的功能就好像是一个命令行版的 Cursor。在命令行的参数里面用自然语言描述要实现的编程任务，它就会调用附带的几种工具，包括运行命令、修改文件等，来利用 Agentic Workflow 实现自我迭代、自我更正。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因此，很多之前因为 Cursor 不提供 API 而很难解决的应用场景，我们可以通过借助 Claude Code 来轻松实现。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(155, 215, 25);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: #327847;\">因此虽然它没有 GUI，看起来对终端用户没有太大吸引力，但是 Claude Code 作为一个基础的 Building Block，则为我们构建很多类似的应用提供了坚实的基础。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">与此同时，在 LaaS 愿景的指导下，它的价值不是让我们能够快速地抄一个 Cursor 出来，而是有潜力推动整个软件开发领域向 LaaS 或者类似的 AI-Native 开发的范式进发。这为彻底改变整个 AI 开发的模式，补全了一块重要的拼图。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">除此之外，Claude Code 还有另一个功能是它可以用 Agentic 的方式调用各种工具，来阅读一个文件夹下面的代码，一步一步构建出一个 Prompt 文件。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它具备的 Agentic 特征让它可以主动探索代码库，并通过对执行过程的动态分析来不断完善、修正对项目的理解。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它就像一个人类实习生，在得到最初的指令后，会自己去读取并分析相关模块，用自然语言描述和工具调用相结合的方式，确认哪部分代码适合复用、哪部分需要改写。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一旦我们在现有系统里完成这样的迁移过程，就等于为 AI 真正打通了与传统代码库的阻隔。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">后续开发新功能或重构旧逻辑时，AI 不需要再次经历同样冗长的学习过程，而是能够直接接管这套自动化工作流，迭代更新成果。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因此，总的来说，Claude Code 的目标是把传统的软件库的使用方式向 AI-Friendly 和 AI-Native 的方向转变，通过提供适当的工具来让这两种迁移更加顺利和无痛。</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:10px 10px 10px 20px;word-spacing:normal;overflow:auto;color:rgb(106, 115, 125);font-weight:400;border-left:3px solid rgb(50, 120, 71);display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding: 0px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);margin: 0px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它背后所拥有的愿景和野心其实远远大于这个简单的命令行工具表面上的价值。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个 AI 统筹所有服务、自动编码、自动调度的世界的雏形，或许已经悄悄地在 Claude Code 身上出现了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种愿景离真正落地还有不少路要走</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，包括对 API 规范的标准化、对安全的策略把控，以及对 Agentic AI 在不同场景下边界与责任划分的探讨。但从 Claude Code 迈出的这一步来看，Anthropic 已经在非常务实地解决一个业界普遍痛点：如何让 AI 更智能地对接旧系统，又如何让旧系统逐渐蜕变为新的 LaaS 形态，从而通往 AI-native 的未来。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">也许这正是 Anthropic 最具前瞻性的地方，却因为没有 Claude 3.7 那么炫目而被很多人忽视。</span></span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:10px 10px 10px 20px;word-spacing:normal;overflow:auto;color:rgb(106, 115, 125);font-weight:400;border-left:3px solid rgb(50, 120, 71);display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding: 0px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);margin: 0px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但我相信，将来大家回头看时，会发现 Claude Code 在这场 AI-native 软件革命里扮演了一个不可替代的起点角色。</span></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;min-height: 20px;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <hr style=\"margin: 15px 0px;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0px 0px;border-color: rgb(50, 120, 71);transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 1);font-size: 15px;\">\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;min-height: 20px;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:10px 10px 10px 20px;word-spacing:normal;overflow:auto;color:rgb(106, 115, 125);font-weight:400;border-left:3px solid rgb(50, 120, 71);display:block;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px;\">\n    <section style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding: 0px;color: rgb(89, 89, 89);margin: 0px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文首发于作者个人网站 Computing Life</span><sup style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">[5]</span></sup></strong></p>\n    </section>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding-left: 0em;min-height: 20px;text-align: left;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin: 10px 0px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;white-space: pre-line;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/55b6b5cc-de50-4d62-ac13-b825e05e6a00/public\" alt=\"loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"border-radius: 8px;font-size: 15px;\" width=\"100%\" data-imgfileid=\"501607246\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/55b6b5cc-de50-4d62-ac13-b825e05e6a00/public\"